{"tid":1298173,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"重要提醒:兄弟爬山","createTime":"2019-07-08T20:14:28.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-09T03:04:10.000Z","uid":236611,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"20a4e80b40f20510d03146d9c4a3d7ed182ec6ea","tid":1298173,"uid":236611,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:14:28.000Z","msg":"唔知點解<br />\n硬係覺得好似步入緊幾年前雨革嘅感覺<br />\n加上頭先一段小插曲<br />\n<br />\n所有人係時候提醒自己可能淡忘左嘅重點<br />\n兄弟爬山，各自努力<br />\n目標一致，槍口對外<br />\n唔好自我分化<br />\n唔好自我感覺良好<br />\n<br />\n一直我地所做所追求既係一件十分嚴肅嘅事<br />\n要記住我地所追求嘅係咩<br />\n作為一個毒撚，用Assasin嘅金句<br />\n&ldquo;Nothing is true everything is permitted&rdquo;<br />\n唯一可以相信嘅係我地既信念<br />\n唯一唔可以破壞嘅亦係我地嘅信念<br />\n其他咩差都係可行<br />\n無論係和理非，定真勇武，定why not both<br />\n依條路真係要我地「一齊走」<br />\n<br />\n雖然係好撚老土<br />\n但我就係你，你就係我<br />\n無你就無我，反之亦然<br />\n是他也是你<br />\n我無嘢講"},{"pid":"d327219101afe911d6879da793a51db4ac565dc8","tid":1298173,"uid":192971,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:15:49.000Z","msg":"<strong><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point1.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />不談判 不犧牲 不分化 不割蓆 不篤灰 不譴責<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/point2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span></strong>"},{"pid":"d40f860ec88985239a255f1b37f23978cfbc1fa1","tid":1298173,"uid":171678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:20:15.000Z","msg":"總之點都要留住條命<br />\n齊上齊落"},{"pid":"c86a401d125c7ff4fd12b1fc6b2024b90e296bda","tid":1298173,"uid":192971,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d40f860ec88985239a255f1b37f23978cfbc1fa1","tid":1298173,"uid":171678,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:20:15.000Z","msg":"總之點都要留住條命<br />\n齊上齊落"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-08T20:25:32.000Z","msg":"我冇野講<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/aura.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76654dc03931399b1bf49ac7eb2d50df862a2319","tid":12